\begin_layout Plain Layout
Quality assurance is a line in the budget.
 Usually not a lot was written in this line because they had not milk analyzers
 to calibrate.
 However, now that machines are there, there is something that can be monitored,
 so this also means that more can be allocated in the budget.
 To help with this, we were asked to provide DDA with a detailed costing
 of calibration.
\end_layout

